title: Skana Robotics unveils Alligator autonomous amphibious vessel
description:
The Alligator is an autonomous amphibious vessel designed to deliver logistics, sensors, and personnel between water and land.

The post Skana Robotics unveils Alligator autonomous amphibious vessel appeared first on The Robot Report.
